erience,\n-A group of learning partners with different personalities will accompany you on your exploration journey\n-Complete learning, feedback and progress system\n-This function of wrong questions strengthens the learning effect\n-Score challenge and hit the excellent learning record of this course!\n\nCome join MageVR!", "short_description": "MageVR-Knowledge and connection are everywhere!\n\nMageVR is a virtual learning platform. We integrate different subjects and knowledge into our content design. Both native speakers and non-native speakers can use MageVR To find interesting and rich learning content, we hope to use VR to redefine the way you acquire knowledge from this world, and at the same time bring you a unique learning experience!"}]}, "developer_name": "Haopeng Yang", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.yumpu.com/s/B2f6jvgKUqeyXYcI", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Haopeng Yang", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.dengxianvr.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPLORATION", "EDUCATIONAL", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "322787426528287"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974864_832472680682260_3128598979071795485_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=eUGvEA9C7AIQ7kNvgEjU2Go&_nc_ht=scontent-i